<h1 itemprop="name">
Krita
</h1>
<p class="lead">
Professional, open-source raster graphics editor with advanced digital painting and sketching tools...
<span class="creator">
<a rel="nofollow" data-link-action="Creator Link" class="ga_outgoing" target="_blank" href="https://krita.org" title="Go to KDE Official site">Created by KDE</a>
</span>
</p>
<ul class="labels">
<li>
<span class="label label-pricing">
<span class="pricing-free">Free</span>
 <span class="oss-label">Open Source</span>
</span>
</li>
<li class="label label-default ">Mac</li>
<li class="label label-default ">Windows</li>
<li class="label label-default ">Linux</li>
<li class="label label-default ">PortableApps.com</li>
<li>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
