<li data-alternativeName="GIMP" data-mainitemid="38d75775-8282-4fd6-a2ff-b04f32938f2f" data-urlname="gimp" id="item-gimp">
<article class="row app-list-item">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-10 col-md-11 col-lg-12">
 <h3>
<a data-link-action="Alternatives" href="/software/gimp/">GIMP</a>
</h3>
<p class="text">
GIMP is a free program for such photo retouching, image composition and image authoring. Essentially it&#39;s the closest thing to Photoshop you can get for free. </p>
<ul class="opinion-comments">
<li class="opinion-note status-Approved">
<div class="note-icon-container warning-color-bg">
<i class="custom-icon-attention-circled note-icon"></i>
</div>
<span class="note">GIMP is for photo editing. Krita is for digital drawing.</span>
<span class="meta">
Guest
• <span title='2019-03-25 3:22:00 AM'>Mar 2019</span>
• 20 agrees and 6 disagrees
</span>
<span data-voteid="778233" class="meta opinion-vote">
