<li class="opinion-note status-Approved">
<div class="note-icon-container warning-color-bg">
<i class="custom-icon-attention-circled note-icon"></i>
</div>
<span class="note">GIMP is for photo editing and not designed for actual digital drawing. Krita is for digital drawing and graphic design.</span>
<span class="meta">
Guest
• <span title='2019-11-15 7:27:00 PM'>6 days ago</span>
