<article class="row app-list-item">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-10 col-md-11 col-lg-12">
<h3>
<a data-link-action="Alternatives" href="/software/mypaint/">MyPaint</a>
</h3>
<p class="text">
MyPaint is a fast, distraction-free, and easy painting tool for digital artists. It supports graphics tablets made by Wacom, and many similar devices. </p>
