<h4><a href="/" class="brand-footer"><img src="/assets/images/logo-new.svg" /></a></h4>
<p>AlternativeTo is a free service that helps you find better alternatives to the products you love and hate.</p>
<p>The site is made by <a rel="nofollow" href="/user/ola">Ola</a> and <a rel="nofollow" href="/user/markus">Markus</a> in Sweden, with a lot of help from our friends and colleagues in Italy, Finland, USA, Colombia, Philippines, France and contributors from all over the world. That's right, all the lists of alternatives are crowd-sourced, and that's what makes the data powerful and relevant.</p>
<p>Feel free to send us your questions and feedback on <a href="mailto:hello@alternativeto.net">hello@alternativeto.net</a>, in our <a rel="nofollow" href="/discussions/">discussion forums</a>, in our <a href="https://discord.gg/VS45yNS">Discord channel</a> or tweet us at <a rel="nofollow" href="https://twitter.com/alternativeto">@AlternativeTo</a></p>
